  <archetypedescription>
    <p>
      The end of times is upon us brothers.   All we have left is
      to meet our makers on terms of our own choosing; fighting
      against the darkness or cowering in our beds.  May
      the gods give us strength to hold our course.
    </p>

    <!--
    <figure>
      <img src="./resources/halfling_rascal.jpg"/>
    </figure>
    -->
    
    <p>
      Black Coats are itinerant preachers that have eschewed the
      bureaucratic, and often corrupt, church organizations in order
      to take the message of the gods directly to the people.
      <!--
      Trade off aspects from their gods for their spell dice.

      e.g. 
      purge the unclean
      by the letter of the book
      holy number of X
      aescetic.. keeps almost no money.
      shed no blood
      chaste

      Get thee hence.      
      God provides.. roll to have a required item.
      aspect... Shed no blood - Not a drop by mine hand.
      -->
    </p>
  </archetypedescription>

